reactor.netty.incubator.quic

Class QuicClientConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • reactor.netty.transport.TransportConfig
      • reactor.netty.incubator.quic.QuicClientConfig

  • public final class QuicClientConfig
extends TransportConfig
    Encapsulate all necessary configuration for QUIC client transport. The public API is read-only.
    Author:
    Violeta Georgieva
